J.D. BUTLER, an individual, Plaintiff-Appellant, v. Donald H. RUMSFELD, Secretary of Defense, Department of Defense, Defendant-Appellee. No. 05-55223. United States Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Argued and Submitted March 6, 2007. Filed March 14, 2007. Leodis C. Matthews, Esq., Matthews & Partners, Los Angeles, CA, for Plaintiff-Appellant. *461Thomas K. Buck, Esq., USLA — Office of the U.S. Attorney Civil & Tax Divisions, Los Angeles, CA, for Defendant-Appellee.

Before: RYMER, WARDLAW, and SMITH, Circuit Judges.

MEMORANDUM *

We affirm for the reasons stated by the district court.

AFFIRMED.

This disposition is not appropriate for publication and is not precedent except as provided by 9 th Cir. R. 36-3.
